Interface ConstructClause<T extends AbstractQueryBuilder<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The Builder type that the clause is part of.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConstructBuilder
    public interface ConstructClause<T extends AbstractQueryBuilder<T>>
    Interface that defines the ConstructClause as per http://www.w3.org/TR/2013/REC-sparql11-query-20130321/#rConstructTemplate
